<paragraph id="820B36BEFFC8FFA3FF7BF973FB8BF955" blockId="116.[189,1398,1711,1775]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">
Thirty-five species. Endemic in C and E Europe, with two species (
<taxonomicName id="45B44D3DFFC8FFA3FBF2F96CFA91F972" baseAuthorityName="Verhoeff" baseAuthorityYear="1897" box="[1076,1340,1711,1737]" class="Diplopoda" family="Mastigophorophyllidae" genus="Mastigona" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chordeumatida" pageId="116" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bosniensis">
